headline: TD Announces Strategic Relationship with Fiserv to Enhance TD Merchant Solutions Offering in Canada
summary: TD Bank Group ("TD") (TSX: TD) (NYSE: TD) announced today that it has finalized a strategic relationship with Fiserv, a leading global provider of payments and financial services technology, to elevate the client experience within the TD Merchant Solutions business in Canada ("TDMS") and continue bringing best-in-class solutions to its Canadian clients. The relationship will also simplify TDMS and reduce costs, improving financial performance for TD over time.
